---
title: Double Spiced Chicken & Red Wine Jus with Parsnip Mash & Garlic Veggies
description: We’ve had a red wine jus with beef and pork, now it’s time for this herby chicken to have its time drizzled in
this richly flavoured sauce. A fluffy parsnip and potato mash helps to soak up any leftover flavours.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spiced-double-chicken-red-wine-jus-dc9759ee.jpg
